  <!-- Intro -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid-2" style="align-items: start;">
        <div>
          <h2>Independent Funding, Independent Voice</h2>
          <p>As a statutory body under the National Health Service Act 2006, Manchester LMC must be financially independent of NHS England and ICBs. This independence is essential — it means we can represent GPs robustly, without fear or favour, even when that means challenging commissioners or government policy.</p>
          <p>Our funding comes from two sources: a statutory levy on GP practices, and a voluntary subscription for locum and portfolio GPs. Both are modest, transparent, and set by the elected committee.</p>
          <p>We do not receive grants, sponsorship, or income from pharmaceutical companies. We hold no commercial conflicts of interest.</p>
        </div>
