  <!-- Levy model -->
  <section class="section" style="background: var(--colour-neutral);">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="text-center" style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">The Practice Levy</h2>
      <p class="text-center" style="color: var(--colour-muted); max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto 3rem;">Every GP practice holding an NHS contract in Manchester contributes to the LMC through a statutory levy — an obligation set by national legislation.</p>

      <div class="grid-3" style="gap: 2rem;">
        <div class="card" style="text-align: center; padding: 2rem;">
          <div style="width: 64px; height: 64px; background: var(--colour-primary); border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin: 0 auto 1rem;">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.8" aria-hidden="true"><rect x="2" y="7" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M16 7V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v2"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 style="margin: 0 0 0.5rem;">Who Pays</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--colour-muted); margin: 0;">All practices holding a GMS, PMS, or APMS contract within the Manchester area. The levy is calculated in relation to the registered list size and the number of whole-time-equivalent GPs.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card" style="text-align: center; padding: 2rem;">
          <div style="width: 64px; height: 64px; background: var(--colour-primary); border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin: 0 auto 1rem;">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.8" aria-hidden="true"><line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="23"/><path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 style="margin: 0 0 0.5rem;">How It's Set</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--colour-muted); margin: 0;">The levy rate is agreed each year by the elected LMC committee at the Annual General Meeting (AGM), where all member practices have a vote. Rates are set to cover operating costs only — we do not accumulate surpluses.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card" style="text-align: center; padding: 2rem;">
          <div style="width: 64px; height: 64px; background: var(--colour-primary); border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin: 0 auto 1rem;">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.8" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 style="margin: 0 0 0.5rem;">What It Funds</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--colour-muted); margin: 0;">Staffing, committee meetings, representation at regional and national LMC conferences, legal and HR consultation, and the maintenance of guidance, news, and member services for all practices.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Locum subscription -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid-2" style="align-items: center; gap: 3rem;">
        <div>
          <span class="badge badge--accent" style="margin-bottom: 1rem; display: inline-block;">Locum &amp; Portfolio GPs</span>
          <h2 style="margin-top: 0;">Voluntary Subscription</h2>
          <p>Locum GPs, portfolio GPs, and those not working within a contracted practice are not covered by the practice levy — but they still have access to everything Manchester LMC offers, including confidential advisory services, wellbeing support, and access to our guidance library.</p>
          <p>To support this, we offer a voluntary annual subscription of <strong>£100 per year</strong>. Subscribers receive full member benefits:</p>
          <ul style="color: var(--colour-text); line-height: 2;">
            <li>Access to the subscriber-only area (agenda papers, meeting minutes, open forum)</li>
            <li>Confidential advisory support from the Managing Director</li>
            <li>Representation at the LMC and at national conferences</li>
            <li>Regular newsletters and updates</li>
            <li>Access to all guidance documents and resources</li>
            <li>Invitation to LMC meetings and events</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/members/#register" class="btn btn--accent" style="margin-top: 1rem;">Register as a Subscriber</a>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="card" style="padding: 2rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--colour-accent);">
            <p style="font-size: 3rem; font-family: var(--font-heading); font-weight: 700; color: var(--colour-accent); margin: 0 0 0.25rem;">£100</p>
            <p style="font-weight: 600; color: var(--colour-primary); margin: 0 0 1rem;">per year</p>
            <p style="color: var(--colour-muted); margin: 0 0 1.5rem;">Full member access for locum and portfolio GPs not covered by the practice levy.</p>
            <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0 0 1.5rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; color: var(--colour-text); font-size: 0.9rem;">
