        <p>Manchester LMC operates in accordance with a written constitution that sets out our statutory basis, the composition and election of the committee, meeting procedures, financial governance, and the rights of member practices.</p>
        <p>The constitution was last updated in 2022 in line with changes to NHS organisational structures following the Health and Care Act 2022 and the formation of Greater Manchester Integrated Care Board.</p>

